    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Verify Your Account</title>
    <style>
        p {
            font-size: 12px;
        }
        .warning {
            color: red;
            font-size: 10px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h2>Hello {{ name }}</h2>
    <p>You have created an account to use with our Scheduling Workbox System applications. Please verify your account by clicking the following link: <a href={{ activation }} title='Activate'>Activate</a>.</p>
    <p class="warning">If you did not create any account to one of our applications, we strongly recommend you not to click any links in this message!</p>
    <p>
        Thank you
        <br>The Scheduling Workbox System team
    </p>
</body>
</html>